high_descs: Turn right and right again, walk to the microwave.
Take the mug out of the microwave.
Turn left and walk to the sink.
Wash the mug in the left part of the sink.
Take a step left to the coffee maker.
Place the cup in the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed cup in a coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the microwave to your right.
Open the microwave and grab the cup inside.
Carrying the cup, turn around and place it in the sink to your right.
Turn on the water, wash the cup, then remove the cup.
Carrying the clean cup, walk to the coffee maker to your left.
Place the clean cup on the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean cup on the coffee maker.

high_descs: Go to the microwave on your right.
Remove the mug that's inside the microwave.
Walk to the left kitchen sink.
Soak the mug completely in the sink, and grab it.
Walk to the coffee machine on the left.
Place the mug under the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Clean a used mug to make coffee.
